食天山雪蓮、紅景天、青蘭等藥用植物（。。。）但因為環境劣化，要被逼食草中。數量目前大約只有1000隻，就快絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似啤啤熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DfXyo7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfXyo7k.jpg&h=fb98c73e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKKH1T1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKKH1T1.jpg&h=2907685e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH9XQNn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH9XQNn.jpg&h=41f293aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5748aaa08cec5c8a79e384db828dc4880ee6c3b1","tid":1882063,"uid":284901,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"蜜袋鼯，又叫飛天鼠，可以飛天，雜食但十分嗜甜。體型迷你，眼大水汪汪。<br />\n<br />\n我摸過一隻嘢一次，個身同條尾好軟淋淋，樣好得意，會係人身上爬來爬去，鍾意捐入口袋、衫。雖然好可愛但好難養。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWK5fkT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWK5fkT.jpg&h=c8a3974a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJiBm0T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJiBm0T.jpg&h=23256993&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkC6Kee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkC6Kee.jpg&h=c75176b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwhiAkV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwhiAkV.jpg&h=3877d883&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01c50918ad3d3a300a7ebe6ae3f662e8b8671dae","tid":1882063,"uid":263910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T18:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"