.000Z","msg":"野味"},{"pid":"f424f89297a94db793292dd9c73f8a43f555309e","tid":1882063,"uid":28771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:45:51.000Z","msg":"鄰國人：正，有新品種野味食！"},{"pid":"14c4f30586e68bac79baba110bf6785d901aa407","tid":1882063,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:59:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得係老鼠同埋兔仔<br />\n<br />\n尤其是蛋形嗰種身體"},{"pid":"f72cd5a3eb081c6fddf8e5923da16fe40730a740","tid":1882063,"uid":44277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C0UMRiL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC0UMRiL.png&h=98954c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A30TwiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA30TwiM.png&h=c4a5cd20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vBfKDN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vBfKDN.jpg&h=ddd036cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPUAKDN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPUAKDN.jpg&h=a368162b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名稱<br />\nDik-dik（小羚, 犬羚, 迪克小羚羊）<br />\n<br />\nDik-dik 這個名字真改得好，因為牠們真是很「的式」的。<br />\n洋人當然不會用廣東俗語來為這小動物命名。Dik-dik 的名稱來自小羚遇到危險時發出的 &quot;zik ... zik&quot; 的聲音。雌性的體型通常較雄性大，但只有雄性有細少而向後的小角。<br />\n牠們很害羞膽小，很多時會夜間才活動。我第一次在東非 safari 的嚮導很壞，明知牠們膽小還刻意大力開關車門嚇牠們。<br />\n<br />\n分布<br />\n南非及東非的灌木林地。"},{"pid":"7370108116c6b50b0ae1042a141874d81ffe7ca2","tid":1882063,"uid":177150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6672486d79b6ce6ca098593b79242f7b14877a8d","tid":1882063,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"銀喉長尾山雀"},{"pid":"e8dafc3b53a0818944bb78b4a59541861a8a2253","tid":1882063,"uid":173191,"lik